title: Bug 121170: get column label from meta data object should return recognizable strings
OB: When retrieving column labels from the meta data object, the labels returned before extraction are null. However, after extraction, the labels are recognizable strings.
SR:
1. Retrieve meta data object.
2. Attempt to get the column labels from the meta data object.
3. Notice that the labels returned are null.
4. Extract the meta data object.
5. Repeat step 2 to get the column labels.
6. Observe that the labels are now recognizable strings.
